{"type":"message","id":"1d11b9c9","parentId":"fd306c97","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:04:41.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6twfpakpw86w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1376,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777334681492}}
{"type":"message","id":"7430bf40","parentId":"1d11b9c9","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:04:41.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6twfpakpw86w_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1385,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777334681493}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f11f126","parentId":"7430bf40","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:04:50.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough info. Let me send both messages.\n\nGmail has 1 new email:\n- Aventine Northshore daily digest - LOW PRIORITY (promotions/category updates)\n\niCloud has 4 emails but some are read. Let me check the flags - 9 is unread (⚠️ action needed), 8 is read (R), 7 is read (R), 6 is read (R). So only email 9 is new/unread.\n\nWait, the flags show:\n- 9: no flags (unread, no reply)\n- 8: R (read)\n- 7: R (read)\n- 6: R (read)\n\nSo only email 9 is actually new. Let me provide the summaries.\n\n\nFor iCloud, email 9 from RC Leasing is an important reply about apartment availability - they have one that might work for mid-June and it's first come first serve, so I should flag that for attention.","thinkingSignature":"23d9ea3d65c461535faf0eaf86ae2155563b526c4d92e483805c1a1c095bfda1"},{"type":"text","text":"📬 **GMAIL — New Mail (1 new)**\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• Aventine Northshore — Daily Digest for 4/27/26\n  └ Your daily apartment community digest from RealPage\n\n---\n\n📬 **ICLOUD — New Mail (1 new)**\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ ⚠️ Amy says they may have a unit for your timeframe — first come, first serve. Reply once Logan completes his app to begin the process."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1590,"output":311,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20937,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777334681495,"responseId":"063f2c999319a634f7d872a450a08464"}}
